{"tid":419903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【升旗禮】社民連示威：人民未當家 沒有國慶只有國殤","createTime":"2017-10-01T01:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T02:36:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d367c3c4e6aa92473eb57333795f87f328a6c30","tid":419903,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57277127&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57277127%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171001&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2FjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=78854a20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57277127%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171001&h=edd810f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57277127&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171001</a><br />\n<br />\n【升旗禮】社民連示威：人民未當家 沒有國慶只有國殤<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-10-01 08:42:38 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171001/large/1506818737_fa29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171001%2Flarge%2F1506818737_fa29.jpg&h=844021d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱永倫攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n今年10.1國慶日，社民連一如往年，早上發起示威。社民連「長毛」梁國雄、吳文遠、曾健成、社運人士古思堯、「女長毛」雷玉蓮等均有參與。他們拿著「人民未當家，沒有國慶；六四未平反，只有國殤」的橫額；遊行人士亦各自手握「停止軟禁劉霞」、「維權律師無罪，釋放江天勇」等標誌。<br />\n<br />\n長毛在出發前表示，黃浩銘這位戰友因為與黃之鋒等傘運參與者仍在監獄服刑，今年國慶未能參與示威，希望他盡快歸隊。長毛帶領在場示威者高呼「雨傘運動無罪」、「釋放黃之鋒」等口號以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n今早警方亦未有怠慢，最少4輛警車、30名警員沿著灣仔軒尼詩道佈防。示威隊伍走到會展外的會議道與菲林明道交界便停下。<br />\n<br />\n長毛在宣讀聲明時表示，政府窮政權的力量，逼迫傘運領袖，實受內地政府所主使，亦是未來港人命運的寫照，呼籲市民下午出席維園遊行，反威權政治。他隨著呼叫口號時，包括要求「公審江澤民」、「公審李鵬」。他透露，最近一次探望黃浩銘是前日，形容黃相當精神，正忙於學習「好多嘢」，包括英文；他又稱，黃正「寫緊啲嘢」，如文章，詩歌等。"},{"pid":"65a5e97f23127e8470195e8922c174050313c202","tid":419903,"uid":72688,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"點解要落阿爺面"},{"pid":"e9d778d89a5d4d1b1092d97d110ca5d72b9dac07","tid":419903,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:55:25.000Z","msg":"國你老味"},{"pid":"702731cf6adbf97d787a67b8fd581ea5e0d92b27","tid":419903,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"又係呢幾條廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db7f090354421f20c5d931e8c6675dab91fde62","tid":419903,"uid":70946,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢幾條廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯，年輕有為嘅都係坐喺屋企指點江山，運籌帷幄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8542cf7bc9d6a83d5dffc669c1048c573434e20b","tid":419903,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bf391e3f6ef0d1b9620a476df972db3139b889c","tid":419903,"uid":72688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"隔離國家國慶關我哋香港人撚事，你班老嘢咁鍾意中國點解唔去中國住"},{"pid":"59666c23086b3b8756b365797a5771d9936579dc","tid":419903,"uid":6211,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離國家國慶關我哋香港人撚事，你班老嘢咁鍾意中國點解唔去中國住</blockquote><br />\n唔關你事，但有公眾假期<br />\nd街鋪頭掛哂國旗<br />\n夜晚仲有放埋煙花<br />\n<br />\n唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcc85e13b531ec51f01b17b1b33d029212d9f66","tid":419903,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離國家國慶關我哋香港人撚事，你班老嘢咁鍾意中國點解唔去中國住</b